verbose_text: In the C2C12 muscle cells, treatment with GPE at 2.5 mug/ml significantly decreased CAT activity by 12.7, 14.5 and 19.5% at the 12, 18 and 24 h time points, respectively compared to the control (XREF_FIG), while treatment with GPE at 10 mug/ml decreased CAT activity by 8.3, 21.0 and 26.1% at the 12, 18 and 24 h time points, respectively compared to the control (XREF_FIG).
